======
README
======

Instructions for dealing with Translations are in the wiki:

https://develop.participatoryculture.org/trac/democracy/wiki/TranslationGuide

Summary
=======

Upload to Launchpad
-------------------

Run ``build-messages.sh`` to build the ``messages.pot`` file to upload to 
Launchpad.


Download from Launchpad
-----------------------

Run ``build-catalgos.py`` to fix ``.po`` files and other issues and then
generate the ``.mo`` files.
